1. *Razmišljao* sam o tome celu noć. (I have been *thinking* about it all night.)
2. Da li *razmišljaš* o svojoj budućnosti? (Are you *thinking* about your future?)
3. Oni ne žele da *razmišljaju* o tome. (They don't want to *think* about it.)
4. *Razmišljajmo* o tome zajedno. (Let's *think* about it together.)
5. Kada *razmišljam* o tebi, uvek se nasmejem. (When I *think* about you, I always smile.)
6. Oni su *razmišljali* o svom odgovoru. (They *thought* about their response.)
7. Molim te, *razmišljaj* pre nego što govoriš. (Please, *think* before you speak.)
8. Da li si ikada *razmišljao* o promeni posla? (Have you ever *considered* changing jobs?)
9. Moramo dobro *razmišljati* pre nego što donesemo odluku. (We need to *think carefully* before making a decision.)
10. Nemoj da mi *razmišljaš* umesto mene. (Don't *think* for me.)